#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:2
msgid "容器"
msgstr "Containers"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:4
msgid ""
"常见的Java服务器有Tomcat、Weblogic、JBoss、GlassFish、Jetty、Resin、IBM "
"Websphere等，这里对部分框架做一个简单的说明。"
msgstr ""
"Common Java servers include Tomcat, WebLogic, JBoss, GlassFish, Jetty, "
"Resin, and IBM WebSphere. This section briefly describes some of them."

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:7
msgid "Tomcat"
msgstr "Tomcat"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:8
msgid "Tomcat是一个轻量级应用服务器，在中小型系统和并发访问用户不是很多的场合下被普遍使用，用于开发和调试JSP程序。"
msgstr "Tomcat is a lightweight application server. It is widely used in small and medium-sized systems and scenarios with modest concurrent user counts, and is commonly used to develop and debug JSP programs."

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:10
msgid "在收到请求后，Tomcat的处理流程如下："
msgstr "After receiving a request, Tomcat processes it as follows:"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:12
msgid "客户端访问Web服务器，发送HTTP请求"
msgstr "The client accesses the Web server and sends an HTTP request"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:13
msgid "Web服务器接收到请求后，传递给Servlet容器"
msgstr "After receiving the request, the Web server passes it to the Servlet container"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:14
msgid "Servlet容器加载Servlet，产生Servlet实例后，向其传递表示请求和响应的对象"
msgstr "The Servlet container loads the Servlet, creates a Servlet instance, and passes it objects representing the request and response"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:15
msgid "Servlet实例使用请求对象得到客户端的请求信息，然后进行相应的处理"
msgstr "The Servlet instance uses the request object to obtain the client's request information and then performs the corresponding processing"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:16
msgid "Servlet实例将处理结果通过响应对象发送回客户端，容器负责确保响应正确送出，同时将控制返回给Web服务器"
msgstr "The Servlet instance sends the processing result back to the client through the response object. The container ensures that the response is sent correctly and returns control to the Web server"

#: ../../source/language/java/container.rst:18
msgid "Tomcat服务器是由一系列可配置的组件构成的，其中核心组件是Catalina Servlet容器，它是所有其他Tomcat组件的顶层容器。"
msgstr "A Tomcat server consists of a series of configurable components. The core component is the Catalina Servlet container, which is the top-level container for all other Tomcat components."

